headline.print_headline: Egypt Calls for Indefinite Ceasefire in Gaza
headline.main: Egypt Calls for Indefinite Ceasefire in Gaza

lead_paragraph: Egypt called on Israel and the Palestinians on Saturday to accept an indefinite ceasefire and resume indirect talks in Cairo to end the Gaza crisis, Egypt's foreign ministry said in a statement.
